snippet.title: 🪐 Star Trucker 🪐 I Launch Trailer - Available NOW on Steam and Xbox Series S/X
snippet.description:
An interstellar twist on the truck sim genre! Hop into the driver's seat of your rocket-powered big rig as you haul cargo, scavenge for salvage and interact with an eclectic cast of star-hopping truckers. 

Star Trucker is available now on Steam and Xbox Series S/X (Day One with Game Pass). The ultimate open road is waiting!

Steam: https://bit.ly/3KMBeAL
Xbox: https://bit.ly/3yVPmET
